        "<a href=\"https://colab.research.google.com/github/ThulaganyoMathiba-Port/Project-Thulaganyo/blob/main/This%20is%20my%20first%20beautifulsoup%20appliation\" target=\"_parent\"><img src=\"https://colab.research.google.com/assets/colab-badge.svg\" alt=\"Open In Colab\"/></a>"
